User types 1. Admin : Admin will have access to everything including user_management, and bank and branch management 2. Manager: Can add/edit/delete a user, add/edit/delete loans which belongs to their branch and their bank branch users and added loans ,specific to their branch. search loans of all banks and branches across network. 3. User: Can view/add/edit their own added loans not others in their specific bank branch, can search loans across all banks and branches.
